description: Eliminate pet odors with ODORx Un-Duz-It Unleashed Pet Odor and Pet Stain Remover and Odor Eliminator. ODORx Un-Duz-It odor and pet stain remover combines stain and odor removing oxidizers with soil digesting enzyme action, plus odor encapsulants to remove the toughest pet urine odors and stains. Formulated to easily pour on stains, let sit and extract, this professional cleaning solution is ideal for use in large spaces like homes, multi-resident buildings and hotels. This enzymatic cleaner for dog urine works on virtually any water-cleanable surface. ODORx Un-Duz-It Unleashed Pet Odor Enzyme Stain Remover makes a great carpet stain remover, upholstery stain remover, urine stain remover and even a concrete stain remover. Count on Un-Duz-It Unleashed for thorough and effective stain removal. ODORx also offers a variety of other products for odor removal, including Pet Urine Odor and Stain Eliminator.
